  "title": "读取配置文件",
  "cells": [
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "data": "### 使用到的注解\n\n@Configuration\n@PropertySource\n\n### 实例代码"
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "language": "c_cpp",
      "data": "@Configuration\n@PropertySource(value = \"classpath:ma.properties\",ignoreResourceNotFound = true)\npublic class Manager {\n\n    @Value(\"${ma.name}\")\n    private String name;\n\n    public String getUser()\n    {\n        return name;\n    }\n\n}"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "data": "### 扩展\n1. 框架默认是扫描resources文件夹中的配置文件\n2. 可以在maven的配置文件pom.xml中修改默认资源文件夹"
